{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 59,
  "title": "第五十九章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "治人事天，莫若嗇。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫唯嗇，是謂早服；"
    },
    {
      "text": "早服謂之重積德；"
    },
    {
      "text": "重積德則無不克，無不克則莫知其極；"
    },
    {
      "text": "莫知其極，可以有國；"
    },
    {
      "text": "有國之母，可以長久；"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂深根固柢，長生久視之道。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "莫若，猶莫過也。嗇，農夫，農人之治田務，去其殊類，歸於齊一也。全其自然，不急其荒病，除其所以荒病，上承天命，下綏百姓，莫過於此。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "早服，常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "唯重積德，不欲銳速，然後乃能使早服其常，故曰早服謂之重積德者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道無窮也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以有窮而莅國，非能有國也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "國之所以安謂之母，重積德是唯圖其根，然後營末，乃得其終也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
